text: Cosmotomidius is a genus of longhorn beetles of the subfamily Lamiinae,Biolib.cz - Cosmotomidius. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. containing the following species: ==Species== * Cosmotomidius cacaoensis Touroult & al., 2010 * Cosmotomidius crudiaphilus Touroult & al., 2010 * Cosmotomidius egregius (Martins & Galileo, 2007) * Cosmotomidius elongatus Touroult & al., 2010 * Cosmotomidius morvanae Touroult & al., 2010 * Cosmotomidius nigrisetosus Touroult & al., 2010 * Cosmotomidius setosus (Audinet-Serville, 1835) * Cosmotomidius vincus Machado & Monné, 2009 ==References== Category:Acanthoderini Category:Cerambycidae genera
